      "writtenOn": "2014-09-25T22:01:17Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "The way isHttpSpace is implemented, this block is happy to accept a method followed by CR or LF. I suggest you redefine isHttpSpace to not match CR or LF. In fact, it should be just SP according to the RFC, but you could include the TAB, just in case.",
      "revId": "c61aa988eaa0eaf073274ca1bf1cf2896e47eace",
      "serverId": "85c56323-6fa9-3386-8a01-6480fb634889",
